query:
INSERT INTO places (atollId, name, code, type)
SELECT 
  ml.atollId,
  ml.name,
  LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ml.slug, '-', '_'), ' ', '_'), '--', '_')),
  'resort'
FROM map_locations ml
WHERE ml.type = 'resort'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE type = type
